<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">Dear <%= @client.name %>,</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  We are pleased to inform you that your task, "<strong><%= @task.title %></strong>," has been accepted by a freelancer on GigHive.
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  The freelancer will commence work on your task shortly. You can view the task details and monitor its progress by clicking the link below:
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  <%= link_to 'View Task on GigHive', task_url(@task), style: 'color: #007BFF; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #007BFF; color: #fff; border-radius: 5px;' %>
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  Should you have any additional instructions or updates for the freelancer, please communicate with them directly through the GigHive platform.
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  Thank you for choosing GigHive to bring your ideas to life!
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  Sincerely,<br>
  The GigHive Team
</p>